n con uno el techo y los bastidores inferiores utilizan otro mucho más elástico y para los refuerzos de la suspensión se utiliza uno al que se le añadieron elementos de aleación detrás de cada pieza de acero hay una tecnología especializada los contenedores para tráiler se fabrican con los de baja aleación para que sean ligeros y a la vez puedan trasportar cargas pesadas este tipo de acero también es utilizado en las vigas para la construcción ya que son delgadas resistentes y con ellas se optimiza el espacio en los edificios herramientas como taladros escariadores fresas o machos de rosca están hechas con aceros aleados y pueden contener elementos como vanadio molibdeno y mayor cantidad de manganeso silicio o cobre que el que llevan la mayoría de los aceros para brindarles una mayor dureza para que un acero sea inoxidable y pueda protegerse contra la herrumbre y la oxidación natural del hierro se le añade cromo y níquel en un porcentaje superior al  por ciento de esta manera puede ser utilizado en maquinaria sofisticada como turbinas de vapor tanques de refinerías de petróleo o en plantas químicas nuestra vida moderna sería impensable sin la existencia del acero la vivienda el transporte de insumos los viajes al espacio la extracción del petróleo y un sinfín de necesidades requieren la resistencia y la dureza propias de este material última actualización el jueves  de diciembre de    quiénes somos historia perfil misión y visión políticas estructura ubicación contacto relación con inversionistas cotización de la acción resultados trimestrales noticias relacionadas recompra inversiones en proceso eventos relevantes sec filings productos y servicios productos distribución captación de chatarra información general acero y vida cotidiana reciclaje av lázaro cárdenas no  col la nogalera cp  guadalajara jalisco tel    aviso de privacidad grupo simec  copyright  todos los derechos reservados powered by pixelsiete grupo simec sab de cv sim company profile  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states profile grupo simec sab de cv sim related topics stocksstock screenerbasic materialssteel overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse sim on american stock exchange usd  jul  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description grupo simec sab de cv incorporated on august   is a manufacturer processor and distributor of special bar quality sbq steel and structural steel products with production and commercial operations in the united states mexico and canada the company operates through two segments mexican and usa the mexican segment includes the plants in mexicali guadalajara tlaxcala and san luis potosi the usa segment includes approximately seven republic steel inc republic plants of which over six are located in the united states distributed in the states of ohio indiana and new york and approximately one in canada ontariothe company produces a range of sbq steel long steel and mediumsized structural steel products in its mexican facilities it produces ibeams channels structural and commercial angles hot rolled bars round square and hexagonals flat bars rebars cold finished bars and wire rods in its the united states facilities the company produces hot rolled bars cold finished bars semifinished tube rounds and other semifinished trade products the companys sbq products are used across a range of engineered enduser applications including axles hubs and crankshafts for automobiles and light trucks machine tools and offhighway equipment its structural steel products are used in the nonresidential construction market and other construction applicationsin the united states and mexico the company owns and operates over  steel making processing andor finishing facilities with a combined annual crude steel installed production capacity of approximately  million tons and a combined annual installed rolling capacity of over  million tons the company operates both minimill and integrated steel making facilities the company owns and operates a minimill in guadalajara jalisco a minimill in mexicali baja california norte a minimill in apizaco tlaxcala a cold finishing facility in cholula puebla approximately two minimills in san luis potosi san luis potosi mexico and a mini mill in canton ohio which is an integrated facility in lorain ohio and rolling and finishing facilities in lorain and massillon ohio lackawanna new york gary indiana memphis tennessee solon ohio and hamilton ontario all of which the company owns through its subsidiary republicibeamsthe companys ibeams also known as standard beams are i form steel structural sections with two equal parallel sides joined together by the center with a transversal section forming degree angles the company produces ibeams in its mexican facilities and they are used by the industrial construction sector as structure supportschannelsthe companys channels also known as ubeams because of their u form are steel structural sections with two equal parallel sides joined together by its ends with a transversal section forming degree angles the company produces channels in its mexican facilities and they are used by industrial construction sector as structure supports and for stocking systemsanglesthe companys angles are two equal sided sections joined by their ends with a degree angle in an l form the company produces angles in its mexican facilities and they are used mainly by the construction and furniture industries as joist structures and framing systemshot rolled barsthe companys hot rolled bars are round square and hexagonal steel bars that can be made of special or commodity steel the construction auto part and furniture industries use the round and square bars the hexagonal bars are made of special steel and are used by the hand tool industry the company produces the steel sections in its mexican and the united states facilitiesflat barsthe companys flat bars are rectangular steel sections that can be made of special or commodity steel the company produces flat bars at its mexican facilities the auto part industry uses special steel as springs and the construction industry uses the commodity steel flat bars as supportsrebarthe companys rebar is reinforced corrugated round steel bars with sections from  to  inches in diameter and the company produced rebar in its mexican facilities rebar is used by the construction industry to reinforce concretecoldfinished barsthe companys coldfinished bars are round and hexagonal sbq steel bars transformed through a diameter reduction process this process consists of reducing the cross sectional area of a bar by drawing the material through a die without any preheating or turning or peeling the surface of the bar the company produces these bars in its mexican the united states and canadian facilities and the auto part industry uses themsemifinished tube roundsthe companys semifinished tube rounds are round bars used as raw material for the production of seamless pipe the semifinished tube rounds are made of sbq steel and the company produces them in its the united states facilities the seamless pipe manufacturers use them to produce pipes used in the oil extraction and construction industriesthe company competes with deacero sa de cv talleres y acero grupo acerero sa de cv nucor corporation arcelor mittal ternium gerdau corsa industrias ch niagara lasalle charter steel steel dynamics inc the timken company commercial metals company thyssenkrupp and gerdau macsteel » full overview of sim company address grupo simec sab de cv edificio a segundo pisoav lazaro cardenas col la nogaleraguadalajara      p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation rufino vigil gonzalez  luis garcia limon  juan jose acosta macias  lourdes ivonne massimi malo  marcos magana rod